survey_response.review_text: Dr. Rohan is a very friendly person and a very learned *** ************* ******* His charges are also very pocket friendly and he makes you feel very comfortable before, during and post the treatment. I would highly recommend going to him for your dental care.

Dr. Rohan is kind, knowledgeable, and does his best to truly care for the patient as a whole. I had some work I needed done before the end of the year, and he moved around his whole schedule just so I could make the deadline. He even explained to me very clearly all the problems with my jaw and how I can prevent future problems from getting worse. He takes his time and makes you feel right at home. And this is coming from someone who hates going to the dentist and has very sensitive teeth. He gives Professional advice, incredibly friendly staff, clean facilities... nothing about which to complain at all. They're very prompt, very thorough, and very cordial. Easily one of the more efficient and helpful clinic I've attended.He was extremely attentive to my needs, asked me questions just to get to know me versus only focusing on my dental needs (he asked a series of questions to understand what kind of headaches I was having when I mentioned I have them frequently). His explanations are thoughtful, he wants you to leave understanding everything that's happened and what needs to happen next. I'll definitely be going back!

My brother and his family always come to Dr Rohan Patni for their teeth problems and are very happy with his skill and professionalism. Based on their recommendations I decided to see you. I must confess that I was totally nervous but I had to get the implant done so I booked  an appointment  but was hesitant /reluctant about showing up. When I sat on the chair I was literally shivering but in no time your patience n tolerance made me feel comfortable and relaxed. The whole experience before and after the procedure was  very smooth n positive. It was painless no swelling or heavy bleeding n it healed fast. I am lucky to be one of your patient. Thank you from the bottom of my heart. Wishing u the best always.
He explained the process well and gave alternative as well . No there doctor would explain things in detail like he did

I would like to express my sincere appreciation to Dr. Rohan for the exceptional care and professionalism demonstrated during my recent dental treatment at Manasi PolyClinic. His expertise and approach made the entire experience extremely positive. Thank you for providing outstanding service!

Alesh
